scenes.description: Takanashi Kiara performs the final song of her 3D Birthday Concert.
Closing credits and a special thank you message to Amelia Watson.
End card with channel subscription information.

subtitles.original: 知らない　いつか夢見た世界が
subtitles.english: I didn't know. The world I once dreamed of

subtitles.original: 閉じる　真っ暗で灯りもない
subtitles.english: is closing. Pitch black, with no light.

subtitles.original: 崩れかけたこの道で
subtitles.english: On this road that's starting to crumble,

subtitles.original: あるはずもないあの時の希望が
subtitles.english: I felt like I saw the hope from back then

subtitles.original: 見えた気がした
subtitles.english: that wasn't even supposed to be there.

subtitles.original: どうして
subtitles.english: Why?

subtitles.original: Black Out Shutter　懐かしい記憶
subtitles.english: Black Out Shutter, nostalgic memories.

subtitles.original: ただ楽しかったあの頃を
subtitles.english: Those days that were just fun.

subtitles.original: Black Out Shutter　でも動けないよ
subtitles.english: Black Out Shutter, but I can't move.

subtitles.original: 闇を駆ける星に願いを
subtitles.english: A wish to the stars racing through the darkness.

subtitles.original: もう一度だけ走るから
subtitles.english: I'll run just one more time.

subtitles.original: 怖くて震える声で呟く
subtitles.english: Whispering with a voice trembling in fear.

subtitles.original: 私の名前を呼んで
subtitles.english: Call my name.

subtitles.original: 夜明けを抱く空　境界線までの
subtitles.english: The sky embracing the dawn, to the boundary line

subtitles.original: 距離あと一歩届かない
subtitles.english: the distance is one step out of reach.

subtitles.original: 堪えた涙が溢れそうなの
subtitles.english: The tears I've held back are about to overflow.

subtitles.original: 今下を向かないで止まってしまう
subtitles.english: Don't look down now, or you'll come to a halt.

subtitles.original: 未来を生きていたいんだ　分かったの
subtitles.english: I want to live for the future. I realized that.

subtitles.original: 思い出して強く強く信じるの
subtitles.english: Remember, and believe strongly, strongly.

subtitles.original: さあ　Black Out Shutter　優しい匂い
subtitles.english: Now, Black Out Shutter, a gentle scent.

subtitles.original: 光を空を飲み込む言葉
subtitles.english: Words that swallow the light, the sky.

subtitles.original: Black Out Shutter　動いてこの足
subtitles.english: Black Out Shutter, move, these feet of mine.

subtitles.original: 世界を超えて
subtitles.english: Go beyond the world.

subtitles.original: 最初から分かっていた
subtitles.english: I knew it from the start.

subtitles.original: ここにいることを
subtitles.english: That I would be right here.

subtitles.original: 私の中の全ての勇気が
subtitles.english: All the courage inside of me

subtitles.original: 火を灯してもう逃げないよ
subtitles.english: lights a fire. I won't run away anymore.

subtitles.original: Black Out Shutter　一人じゃないよ
subtitles.english: Black Out Shutter, I'm not alone.

subtitles.original: 声をあげて泣いたって構わない
subtitles.english: It's okay to raise your voice and cry.

subtitles.original: Black Out Shutter　見ていてくれる？
subtitles.english: Black Out Shutter, will you watch over me?

subtitles.original: 今から始まるの
subtitles.english: It's all starting now.

subtitles.original: 私の物語
subtitles.english: My story.

subtitles.original: 忘れそうになったらこの歌を
subtitles.english: If you're about to forget, this song...

subtitles.original: 歌うの
subtitles.english: ...I will sing.

subtitles.original: Special Thanks to all of KFP, Huke papa, Jenma, best Manager, Kanauru, Gojo, KIRA, Astrophysics
subtitles.english: Special Thanks to all of KFP, Huke papa, Jenma, best Manager, Kanauru, Gojo, KIRA, Astrophysics

subtitles.original: Myth Members: Nenechi, Reine, Subaru, Fauna
subtitles.english: Myth Members: Nenechi, Reine, Subaru, Fauna

subtitles.original: AMELIA WATSON thank you for making this possible, you are so selfless and supportive you made my dream come true and my hard work and suffering worth it! thank you for all that you do for us. Love, Kiara
subtitles.english: AMELIA WATSON thank you for making this possible, you are so selfless and supportive you made my dream come true and my hard work and suffering worth it! thank you for all that you do for us. Love, Kiara

subtitles.original: Thank You for Watching / Please Subscribe!
subtitles.english: Thank You for Watching / Please Subscribe!
